creator: Raptor Maps, Inc.
descriptionHtml: This app is to be used with your Raptor Maps account to view analytics, reports, and maps on a mobile device while in the field. See your location relative to engineering drawings and your solar site's digital twin. Find anomalies faster, add feedback and take inspection notes while in the field.
descriptionShort: View analytics and reports from Raptor Maps.
title: Raptor App

creator: Raptor Maps, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Your solar portfolio has never been easier to analyze and manage - right from your mobile device.

Take your Raptor Maps inspection reports on the go, share with your peers and update report permissions, right in the app.

Walking a site? Leave your paper map in the truck. Your as-built is overlaid on the map, complete with your GPS location.

Aren’t sure where to find that cracked module? This update allows you to locate anomalies in the field right from your device and update their priority with a tap.

Raptor Maps account required. Contact sales@raptormaps.com to set one up today, to schedule your next inspection or as about add on products.
descriptionShort: View analytics and reports from Raptor Maps.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Minor bug fixes and improvements.
